RE/MAX at the Beach / Holden Beach
Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties

data.description: Seize the opportunity to own a cost-efficient slice of paradise on Holden Beach! With island prices on the rise, this 80's model home presents a fantastic chance to invest in a property with excellent potential.  While a touch of updating may enhance its charm, the residence boasts solid construction and a stunning view of the waterway, inviting you to unwind on the porch while watching boats pass by. Nestled in a small community on the quiet back side of the island, the property provides a peaceful retreat with proximity to the beach and escape from main traffic. Featuring 3 bedrooms, a spacious living area with water views, a galley kitchen with abundance of counter space and cabinets, and an enclosed ground level with a garage and laundry room, this home presents a canvas for personalization. This area can be used for your projects or additional storage.  The cozy fenced backyard with a private patio and an outdoor shower completes the picture.  Never rented and lovingly enjoyed by the original owner, this gem is a rare find in the family-friendly atmosphere of Holden Beach, centrally located between Myrtle Beach, SC, and Wilmington, NC.  Explore the possibilities and envision coastal living at its finest!
